caller_intent: A customer needs to add a newly purchased vehicle to their insurance policy, as facilitated by Liliana from Modern Chevrolet.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledges the request for adding a vehicle to a policy.
Agent offers to transfer the call to a specialist for further assistance.
knowledge_required: Understanding insurance policy updates for vehicle additions
Call transfer procedures for specialized support
summary: Liliana from Modern Chevrolet contacts Alliance Insurance to add a newly purchased vehicle to a customer's policy. The agent confirms the request and offers to transfer the call to a specialist, with the customer placed on hold.
